                                        (d)

Investigations of rivers and other streams;
                                        (e)

Utilization of land;
                                        (f)

Parks.

frus:attachment.p:
The harbor office shall be established under the bureau of police,
                                and shall have the following duties: 
                                    1.

Marking sea courses;
                                    2.

Marine policing;
                                    3.

Harbor quarantine;
                                    4.

Dredging of harbors;
                                    5.

Fixing buoys;
                                    6.

Other matters connected with harbor activities.
